  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A combination of movement and a shield bash. <br />Triggers a vs Test of Strength +20 against the target's Strength/Dexterity. On attacker's success, pushes the target 1 hex, deals 2d4 damage (ignores Armor) with 35% chance to Stagger. <br />At a MoS of 25 or higher, you may roll an additional +2d4 damage and push the target up to 2 more hexes. <br />At a MoS of 50 or higher, also knocks the target Prone.<br /><br />You must be at least 2 hexes away from the target.</p>",
